https://github.com/iovisor/bcc/blob/master/docs/reference_guide.md

1. Run the icmp container (you could use any other container that we created):
   - sudo docker run -u root -v /sys/kernel/debug:/sys/kernel/debug:Z --privileged icmp-blocker-xdp:1.0 bash
   - Get another shell: sudo docker exec -it  <ctr-name> bash
2. cd /bcc/tools
   - python3 opensnoop.py
3. Some of the tools you could explore: exitsnoop, runqlat, execsnoop, wakeuptime, tcptop
4. Each tool has a detailed README attached in the same folder: <tool-name>_example.txt 
	
